Well some of the problem is also... while yes it might give you a lot of combat stats it also has a ramp time making it potentially a bit clunky and somewhat unreliable 

And there is also the problem that it doesn't really give any utility like the slow + speed from {{item:3153}}  or the movement speed and burst from {{item:3078}} 

And it has a bit of a clunky build path for an early item... and it isn't all that slot efficient for a late game item
